data.description: PRICED TO SELL FAST! MOTIVATED SELLER! Introducing a meticulously updated and thoughtfully designed property that's perfect for modern living. This spacious single family home features numerous upgrades and amenities that truly set it apart: Brand New HVAC System, New Water Softener, The kitchen has been completely renovated, featuring new appliances, including a microwave, stove, and dishwasher. A walk-in pantry,  and a large kitchen sink make this a culinary haven. The master bathroom boasts double sinks, and a well-organized closet system enhances convenience, spacious living room, High ceilings and recessed lighting create an open, airy feel throughout. The entire interior has been freshly painted, offering a clean and inviting atmosphere.  This property combines style, comfort, and convenience, offering a true haven for contemporary living. Equipped with a solar system large enough to power your electric vehicle, reducing energy costs. - Security and Smart Features: Your peace of mind is assured with a comprehensive security system and cameras, including a doorbell camera. Smart keypads and light switches add convenience and control. Landscaping and Turf: A well-maintained yard with lush landscaping and artificial turf ensures easy maintenance. The exterior was painted in 2019, keeping the property looking sharp and well-maintained. Conveniently placed outlets for your holiday decorating needs. - Garage Key Pad: Easy access to your garage with a keyless entry system. - Boat or RV Parking: Ample space for your recreational vehicles.  Outdoor Oasis: Unwind in your backyard gazebo, surrounded by beautiful landscaping Enjoy the serenity of walking distance to the lake and Mojave Narrows. Centrally located near schools, restaurants, shopping centers, and all your daily needs. - Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
